### ============================================================
### AUTH
### ============================================================

### Registrar primer usuario (onboarding completo)
### Crea: usuario admin + rol ADMIN + permisos + sucursal principal + horarios
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Administrador",
  "last_name": "Principal",
  "email": "admin@mitienda.com",
  "is_owner": true,
  "phone": "+525551234567",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "branch_name": "Mi Tienda Centro",
  "branch_address": "Calle Morelos 45, Centro",
  "branch_phone": "+525551112222",
  "branch_email": "centro@mitienda.com",
  "branch_latitude": 19.432608,
  "branch_longitude": -99.133209
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mitienda.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###

### Obtener perfil del usuario autenticado (requiere token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Asignar permiso a un rol
POST {{baseUrl}}/permissions/roles/{{roleId}}/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permission_id": "REPLACE_WITH_PERMISSION_ID"
}

###

### Ver permisos de un rol
GET {{baseUrl}}/permissions/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Quitar permiso de un rol
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/permissions/roles/{{roleId}}/permissions/REPLACE_WITH_PERMISSION_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================================
### BRANCHES (SUCURSALES)
### ============================================================

### Crear una sucursal
### Cuando se crea una sucursal nueva, automaticamente se crean los permisos para el ADMIN y los horarios
POST {{baseUrl}}/branches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sucursal Secundaria",
  "address": "Calle Secundaria 13, Secundaria",
  "latitude": 19.432608,
  "longitude": -99.133209,
  "phone": "+525551112222",
  "email": "secundaria@mitienda.com",
  "rfc": "EKU9003173C9",
  "is_accepting_orders": true,
  "has_delivery": true,
  "has_pickup": true,
  "delivery_fee": 50.00,
  "delivery_min_amount": 250.00,
  "delivery_radius_km": 10.0
}

###

### Obtener todas las sucursales
GET {{baseUrl}}/branches

###

### Obtener una sucursal por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/branches/{{branchId}}

###

### Actualizar una sucursal
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/branches/{{branchId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sucursal Centro Actualizada",
  "phone": "+525553334444"
}

###

### Desactivar una sucursal (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/branches/{{branchId}}

###

### ============================================================
### BRANCH SCHEDULES (HORARIOS)
### ============================================================

### Obtener horarios de una sucursal
GET {{baseUrl}}/branches/{{branchId}}/schedules

###

### Crear/actualizar horario de un día (upsert)
POST {{baseUrl}}/branches/{{branchId}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "day_of_week": "monday",
  "open_time": "09:00",
  "close_time": "21:00",
  "is_closed": false
}

###

### Marcar un día como cerrado
POST {{baseUrl}}/branches/{{branchId}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "day_of_week": "sunday",
  "is_closed": true
}

###

### Eliminar horario de un día
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/branches/{{branchId}}/schedules/REPLACE_WITH_SCHEDULE_ID

###

### ============================================================
### ROLES
### ============================================================

###

### Crear rol MANAGER
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MANAGER",
  "description": "Gerente de sucursal"
}

###

### Crear rol EMPLOYEE
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "EMPLOYEE",
  "description": "Empleado con acceso limitado"
}

###

### Obtener todos los roles
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles

###

### Obtener un rol por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}

###

### Actualizar un rol
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Descripción actualizada del rol"
}

###

### Eliminar un rol
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}

###

### ============================================================
### USERS
### ============================================================

### Crear un usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "first_name": "Juan",
  "last_name": "Pérez",
  "email": "juan.perez@mitienda.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###

### Crear usuario sin sucursal asignada
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "María",
  "last_name": "García",
  "email": "maria.garcia@mitienda.com",
  "password": "Password456!"
}

###

### Obtener todos los usuarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

###

###

### Obtener un usuario por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

###

### Actualizar un usuario
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Juan Carlos",
  "phone": "+525557778888",
  "is_owner": true
}

###

### Asignar rol a un usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role_id": "{{roleId}}"
}

###

### Quitar rol a un usuario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/roles/{{roleId}}

###

### Desactivar un usuario (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

###

### ============================================================
### CATEGORIES
### ============================================================

### Crear una categoría raíz
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "name": "Electrónica",
  "description": "Productos electrónicos y gadgets"
}

###

### Crear una subcategoría
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parent_id": "{{categoryId}}",
  "name": "Smartphones",
  "description": "Teléfonos inteligentes"
}

###

### Obtener todas las categorías
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

###

###

### Obtener una categoría por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}

###

### Actualizar una categoría
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electrónica y Tecnología",
  "description": "Descripción actualizada"
}

###

### Desactivar una categoría (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}

###

### ============================================================
### PRODUCTS
### ============================================================

### Crear un producto
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "category_id": "{{categoryId}}",
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "description": "Smartphone Apple iPhone 15 Pro 256GB",
  "price": 19999.99,
  "stock": 50
}

###

### Crear un producto asignado a sucursal
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "category_id": "{{categoryId}}",
  "name": "Samsung Galaxy S24",
  "description": "Smartphone Samsung Galaxy S24 128GB",
  "price": 14999.99,
  "stock": 30
}

###

### Obtener todos los productos
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

###

### Obtener productos de una sucursal
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?branchId={{branchId}}

###

### Obtener un producto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

###

### Actualizar un producto
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 17999.99,
  "stock": 45
}

###

### Desactivar un producto (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

###

### ============================================================
### ORDERS (PEDIDOS)
### ============================================================

### Crear una orden (pickup)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "type": "pickup",
  "notes": "Sin cebolla en el producto 1",
  "discount_amount": 0,
  "tax_amount": 0,
  "delivery_fee": 0,
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "{{productId}}",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unit_price": 19999.99,
      "discount_amount": 0
    }
  ]
}

###

### Crear una orden (delivery)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "delivery_address_id": "REPLACE_WITH_DIRECTION_ID",
  "type": "delivery",
  "delivery_fee": 50.00,
  "tax_amount": 0,
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "{{productId}}",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unit_price": 14999.99
    }
  ]
}

###

### Obtener todas las órdenes
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders

###

### Obtener órdenes de una sucursal
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?branchId={{branchId}}

###

### Obtener órdenes por status
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?branchId={{branchId}}&status=pending

###

### Obtener una orden por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}

###

### Buscar orden por número
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/number/ORD-REPLACE_WITH_NUMBER

###

### Actualizar status de una orden
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}

###

### Cancelar una orden
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "cancelled",
  "cancelled_reason": "Cliente solicitó cancelación"
}

###

### Archivar una orden (delivered/cancelled)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/archive

###

### ============================================================
### PAYMENTS (PAGOS)
### ============================================================

### Ver pagos de una orden
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payments

###

### Registrar pago en efectivo
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "cash",
  "amount": 39999.98
}

###

### Registrar pago con tarjeta
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "card",
  "amount": 19999.99,
  "reference": "TXN-ABC123456"
}

###

### Pago parcial (combinado efectivo + tarjeta)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "cash",
  "amount": 10000.00
}

###
